\newlabel{fig:pareto}{{3}{4}{Latency--quality tradeoff under asymmetric query compression. The left panel shows the global teacher--student picture; the right panel resolves the low-MRR student regime, where mean pooling provides the first clear recovery}{figure.caption.10}{}}
