\newlabel{tab:ann-results}{{3}{5}{Exact FAISS versus approximate indices on the frozen best student. All rows use the same 55{,}578-query benchmark slice. \texttt {IVF} is the only approximate index that preserves most of the exact-search quality while still reducing mean search latency}{table.caption.11}{}}
